# Build context = images/ for BOTH runner images (see justfile `sandbox-build` /
# `codex-build` and the release workflow's context resolver), and each Dockerfile
# does `COPY runner-lib ./lib` wholesale. Keep the runner-lib unit tests out of
# the shipped images: they are CI-only, and the runner tree is agent-writable in
# the claude image, so anything we ship there is surface we did not need.
**/*.test.mjs
